Wed Apr 26 18:35:53 BST 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Regrab keys on receipt of MappingNotify event

Wed Apr 26 13:01:19 BST 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Make spawn() use find_current_screen()

Wed Apr 26 11:30:04 BST 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Fix build errors/warnings when VWM not defined

Tue Apr 25 19:35:44 BST 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Track vdesk separately on each managed screen

Tue Apr 25 18:42:29 BST 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Remove is_sticky tests when only need to check vdesk

Tue Apr 25 17:00:09 BST 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Only snap against clients on the same screen

Thu Apr 13 16:15:09 BST 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Fix configure requests containing sibling information

Mon Mar 13 12:53:55 GMT 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Move unused variable workarounds after declarations

Tue Mar  7 08:13:59 GMT 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Flesh out some switches with default cases

