  * Wrap client_update_current into select_client

Wed Feb 22 16:40:39 GMT 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Restructure client_update_current()

Wed Feb 22 12:39:48 GMT 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
