Tue Feb 21 16:36:26 GMT 2006  Ciaran Anscomb <evilwm@6809.org.uk>
  * Don't track bounding_shaped
  This is never used outside set_shape and I'm not convinced that
  XShapeQueryExtents refers to the old values.

